569
00:25:10,599 --> 00:25:12,359
Are you doing to meet him?

570
00:25:13,119 --> 00:25:13,559
Yes.

571
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:16,000
But

572
00:25:16,519 --> 00:25:17,200
Mr. Yao

573
00:25:17,200 --> 00:25:19,039
