574
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:20,759
That's exactly why I'm doing it.

575
00:25:24,519 --> 00:25:24,960
Well...

576
00:25:25,359 --> 00:25:26,200
I'll bring you.

577
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:38,920
