has none.

600
00:26:34,559 --> 00:26:35,400
It's Fu Hailian.

601
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:37,000
If I'm not mistaken,

602
00:26:37,599 --> 00:26:38,880
after His Majesty ascended the throne,

603
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:41,359
