627
00:27:24,039 --> 00:27:25,559
He framed your father and your family,

628
00:27:26,599 --> 00:27:28,440
so you want to find some leverage

629
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,279
to bring him down.

630
00:27:29,559 --> 00:27:30,720
