641
00:27:55,279 --> 00:27:56,079
I advise you

642
00:27:56,519 --> 00:27:57,920
not to act rashly either.

643
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:08,680
You give this contract

644
00:28:08,839 --> 00:28:09,759
and the account book

645
