837
00:35:17,599 --> 00:35:19,440
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

838
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:21,280
Of course you didn't mean to.

839
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:22,920
You just don't want me

840
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:25,039
